harter <br />\n你真係可以做唯一一個頹tee人<br />\n<br />\n利申: 堅係見過"},{"pid":"10efe01c9c3fbc38ac8716382b36302d0697b70c","tid":481838,"uid":50663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T15:59:57.000Z","msg":"我公司做it 全公司男同事都要著suit<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48a8f5c01ce3fd154779f7594ccc61c1d7e49f5f","tid":481838,"uid":93900,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:01:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>著suit都要屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n毒撚自己唔夠膽著，就想搞到全世界人都唔好著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n依巴打邏輯 反強姦等於唔夠膽強姦<br />\n反殺人等於唔夠膽殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n林鄭上高登？反一地兩檢等於無膽接受新事物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"348c8109c3e842134bda463c560ee486a468af2e","tid":481838,"uid":87432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/27/224528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F27%2F224528_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=8e7b5b0c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑撚左<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85c0a780d4cd578e7f91d0be7708f0091f17fcc2","tid":481838,"uid":85252,"like":28,"dislike":1,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:02:04.000Z","msg":"由細到大就教話咩著得好係尊重自己尊重人，一啲又話要show Professional，講黎講去都未必講得人入耳<br />\n<br />\n你因應咩場合著咩衫係睇你想達到咩目的<br />\n你想顯得成熟穩重就著suit，著重好細節<br />\n你想顯得柒毒，咪涼鞋底衫爛牛<br />\n你想掩人面目，可以著大眾衫<br />\n<br />\n著suit等於專業，係D老屎忽過份簡化穿搭嘅目的<br />\n要顯得專業，就係一身細節都要執正做好<br />\n打呔要束緊，西裝要啱身，長褲長度同對鞋尖頭圓頭要都要合乎場景中的身份地位，上下身每樣穿搭都要配合顏色<br />\n做得好畀人一絲不苟嘅印象就會有專業的錯覺<br />\n做唔好，好啲就MK仔，再差啲似古惑仔，陰公啲似低能仔<br />\n<br />\n當然有特例，好似神父有袍，好似一下子乜都遮哂，但個份專業在於乾淨同莊嚴，一身打扮包含住嚴肅同歷史感<br />\n如果神父行出黎著到飛輪海咁，拗頸可以話都得，但確實又離開好多人嘅期望<br />\n<br />\n講到底，除非你係個別範疇的專業可以成為該行指標，蓋過一切（例：Steve Jobs），否則唔想太特立獨行，都係跟番大隊穩陣<br />\n但路係人行出黎，柒同型個條界線，如果樓主自命永不過界，咪悉隨尊便<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 首富們可以唔著suit唔代表佢著得cheap，李嘉誠可以戴USD 400嘅錶而唔cheap，係因為佢係李嘉誠唔係隻錶唔cheap<br />\nP.S.2. 早年文化評論人都係西裝多，之後梁文道開始上到一定高度。個別人士都會跟風學佢打扮，好似邵家臻咁。但係柒係型就各自判斷喇<br />\nP.S.3. 樓主可參考下佬訊，啲穿搭細節都幾有趣"},{"pid":"d19447c763546a2e94063c95d2e3ef079a86db6b","tid":481838,"uid":154684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:02:39.000Z","msg":"酒樓部長"},{"pid":"03d662b34ad7544ceedabd94799ae58e18293008","tid":481838,"uid":93900,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:04:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>酒樓部長</blockquote><br />\n專業人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4a2ea5a2c8fbc2d56f2ed4e09e138a7c4337185","tid":481838,"uid":51105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:04:16.000Z","msg":"點解班愛国撚唔著唐裝？"},{"pid":"a9435fd0f545be86067d91d69b82f8a13466998f","tid":481838,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:04:36.000Z","msg":"樓主好快就會問題,<br />\n通常著suit返工嘅人, 都係食物鏈最低層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a7acbf84122dda4ae56036513c28e98953550c","tid":481838,"uid":10726,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:05:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好快就會<span style=\"color: red;\">發現</span>,<br />\n通常著suit返工嘅人, 都係食物鏈最低層<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"6e702c244b5a6b0a00a3dab56c179872b5b5c8a0","tid":481838,"uid":93900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T16:10:37.000Z","msg":"<blockq